fields.question: Where can I stay?
fields.answer:
Here are a selection of hotels near the venue:

## [Ace Hotel](http://www.acehotel.com/newyork) 

**Starting price (excl taxes and fees)**: $230. 

**Address**: 20 W 29th St, New York, NY 10001 (1.3 miles away). 

**Best transportation to NYU**: N,R from 28th street (3 stops) and walk (15 min).

## [Hampton Inn Manhattan-Soho](http://hamptoninn3.hilton.com/en/hotels/new-york/hampton-inn-manhattan-soho-NYCMHHX/index.html)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $230

**Address**: 54 Watts St, New York, NY 10013 (0.6 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (13min)

## [Hyatt Union Square](http://unionsquare.hyatt.com/en/hotel/home.html)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $245

**Address**: 134 Fourth Avenue, New York, NY 10003 (0.7 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (13min)

## [The London, NYC](http://www.thelondonnyc.com/?gclid=CPDczar5p80CFc6dGQodCZEEig&gclsrc=ds)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $330

**Address**: 151 W 54th St, New York, NY 10019 (3.2 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: B,D,E to W4th (17 min)

## [The Marlton Hotel](http://marltonhotel.com/)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $265

**Address**: 5 W 8th Street, New York, NY 10011 (0.2 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (5min)

## [The Mercer](http://www.mercerhotel.com/)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $470

**Address**: 147 Mercer St, New York, NY 10012 (0.5 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (10min) or Bus: M5 (15min)

## [The Standard: East Village](http://www.standardhotels.com/new-york/properties/east-village)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $290

**Address**: 25 Cooper Square, New York, NY 10003 (0.5 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (10min)

## [The Standard: High Line](http://www.standardhotels.com/new-york/properties/high-line)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $313

 **Address**: 848 Washington Street, New York, NY 10014 (1.3 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: A, from 14th and 8th (1 stop) to W4th and walk (17min total)

## [W Union Square](http://www.wnewyorkunionsquare.com/)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $300

**Address**: 201 Park Avenue South, New York, NY 100003 (0.7 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: The N,R (2 stops) and walk (13min total)

## [Walker Hotel: Greenwich Village](http://www.walkerhotel.com/en)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $285

**Address**: 52 West 13th Street, New York, NY, 10011 (0.6 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (12min) or Bus: M1,M2,M3,M5 and walk (11min)

## [Washington Square Hotel](http://washingtonsquarehotel.com/)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $185

**Address**: 103 Waverly Pl, New York, NY, 10011 (0.2 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: Walk (4 min)

## [The Nomad Hotel](https://www.thenomadhotel.com/)

**Starting price (excl. taxes and fees)**: $365

**Address**: 1170 Broadway, New York, NY 10001 (1.3 miles)

**Best transportation to NYU**: N,R from 28th street (3 stops) and walk (15 min)
